user.intro:
I'm Shihao, a junior at Cornell University, studying Computer Science.

I love downhill longboarding, and photography -- but still learning both! I also love hiking, Formula 1, and EDM. My favorite book series is the Three Body Problem. I’m interested in pushing for more startups in deep-tech, silicon, and aerospace to push humanity forward. My previous work has been in the aero sector working with SpaceX and my research labs on distributed software, rockets, CubeSats, and autonomous drones/cars
